title: Farming App (OSRS)
builttext: React, Node.js, Express, JavaScript, Docker, AWS, JSON
abouttext: An inventory generator that that allows users to find their optimum inventory for a farming run. It scrapes their farming level from the Osrs Highscores API, then checks a database of patches, seeds and teleports to deliver their optimal route and inventory. Supports oAuth for sharing with friends.
